data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN 2.875% Welcome to the perfect blend of comfort & convenience in this updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom Tacoma gem, nestled on a generous 6,000sq ft lot. Main level includes dual closet primary BR, kitchen w/large dining area & large living rm! Upstairs you will find a large room w/walk in closet. Partially finished basement W/ potential for additional living space! RV parking, carport, and shed makes organization a breeze. The fully fenced yard and great gardening spaces creates a tranquil oasis, perfect for relaxation, play or entertaining! This location is a commuter's dream, with easy access to I-5, the Tacoma Mall & shopping options just moments away. A/C for hot days & new roof in 2020! Fidelity Home warranty included!
